Facade Components

Facades are the public API of the components plugin. Each facade is a single tiddler you transclude with parameters and customize via `$fill` slots.

Available facades:

- **pills** (`$:/plugins/rimir/components/pills`) — Horizontal selection pills. Multi-select or single-select. Optional filtering. Syncs selection to any tiddler field. Use for: tag selection, filter toggles, option pickers.
- **vtabs** (`$:/plugins/rimir/components/vtabs`) — Vertical tab list with typed elements (sections, actions, links, subcomponents, spacers). Sections collapse/expand. Use for: navigation sidebars, settings panels, tool palettes.

Navigate deeper: llm_help("components/facades/pills"), llm_help("components/facades/vtabs")
